                     <interp inst="t17870523-37-person425" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
             sworn.</p>
               <p>I am a box-maker; I happened to be in the house; I know nothing of the matter; I only heard the money fall.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t17870523-37-person426">
                  RICHARD
                   WENHAM
               <interp inst="t17870523-37-person426" type="surname" value="WENHAM"></interp>
